sequenceDiagram
    participant Mobile as Mobile App
    participant Main as Main Service
    participant RAG as RAG Service
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB

    Mobile->>Main: POST /guided/clarify
    Main->>RAG: POST /rag/guided-clarify
    RAG-->>Main: topic và câu hỏi làm rõ
    Main-->>Mobile: Danh sách câu hỏi làm rõ
    Mobile->>Main: POST /guided/answer/stream
    Main->>RAG: POST /rag/guided-answer/stream
    RAG-->>Main: progress validate
    Main-->>Mobile: event progress
    RAG->>Chroma: Truy hồi nguồn phù hợp
    RAG-->>Main: progress retrieve, synthesize, verify
    Main-->>Mobile: event progress
    RAG-->>Main: done answer, sources
    Main-->>Mobile: event done
